f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://media.giphy.com/media/Oghyj7b5BLLs4/giphy.gif</a>"},{"pid":"d17e09f67a414075c6e57899327a6c2a02711ce5","tid":617944,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:12:02.000Z","msg":"日本班黑社會會訓練啲細路殺人， 好似係因為 唔使追究法律責任"},{"pid":"8695fd7bb74d4c826821f032641ac08b8213fa08","tid":617944,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc3a4ede2c899dd6ab81232fdf4a6f44943d8ec","tid":617944,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf8531460013173e584ed7e2e078bf447c6aca5","tid":617944,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d196817bcc2938dc501e82f25142d97a1e76c1d6","tid":617944,"uid":48577,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"十歲你扯起都冇5cm 啦 毛都未有條 精你又無得射 你處都破唔到你屌緊人地閪皮炸傻仔"},{"pid":"0714522c74d0f8b72617140b279a73189033c49b","tid":617944,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T13:44:38.000Z","msg":"五毛Me係鬼仔#99568底已起<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/614130/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>事緣: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/590311/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/590311/page/1</a><br />\n會員on99屌喇星開post起鳩個小學雞底 由於睇唔過眼<br />\n亦見到佢自爆左youtube ac, 決定用少少時間試下起佢底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會員on99屌喇星 youtube ac: pc 9527<br />\n竟然連接左google+<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成功左第一步<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/103914_8254a4657f68510fb01fac469b5a9b42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F103914_8254a4657f68510fb01fac469b5a9b42.png&h=b2294ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但咁既資料太唔足夠 亦好容易起錯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再慢慢睇下youtube ac比到D咩我地 發現原來on99屌喇星upload過幾條片<br />\n其中一條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104145_32d3ca5e23f4ccf1e4c8660c40e75f33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104145_32d3ca5e23f4ccf1e4c8660c40e75f33.png&h=2706f2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104151_0a7b8575f81e6d28645879810e6f43a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104151_0a7b8575f81e6d28645879810e6f43a9.png&h=8b057f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信該留言者熟悉片主 亦都透露左pc 9527亦即係on99屌喇星叫Joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我地就開始用google+比既資料去起底 <br />\n首先係Tam Hiu Sze小姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104408_bdd7c437366c101ea2b7ab2f606a469e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104408_bdd7c437366c101ea2b7ab2f606a469e.png&h=84ac15b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左確保無搵錯人 我係Tam Hiu Sze小姐既friend list試下搵唔搵到common friend<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104435_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104435_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=b02aba47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果成功搵到Hoi Kit Leung<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104540_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104540_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=dc576784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再搵到Cody Lam<br />\n<br />\n已經代表無起錯 不過重點主角都係依位叫呀Joe既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104726_bbf4bbb47f12200df3f5be6765c24aad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104726_bbf4bbb47f12200df3f5be6765c24aad.png&h=bb2303cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104734_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104734_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=f2ead5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104740_e29efbe021d12549075b6b01f41993eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104740_e29efbe021d12549075b6b01f41993eb.jpg&h=0a176f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104747_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104747_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=0fc3268b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾位friend list都不約而同有依位Joe Lee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105148_a9fc6e56641b97a4f42197d18d69f16f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105148_a9fc6e56641b97a4f42197d18d69f16f.jpg&h=2fbbbffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Joe Lee friend list亦都有Andy Lee <br />\n咁多資料加埋已經幾肯定會員on99屌喇星就係Joe Lee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再保守D 我地睇埋Joe Lee既Facebook<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105342_49829455611ff6eaed3d12c1c0468dd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105342_49829455611ff6eaed3d12c1c0468dd0.png&h=d40766c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係倫敦讀緊書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105355_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105355_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=5724e527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105411_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105411_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=b7c5f033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦都同會員on99屌喇星一樣好關注時事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後就係會員on99屌喇星出場喇！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105515_20fd42213f37387d37674cc384319170.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105515_20fd42213f37387d37674cc384319170.png&h=cbc40d56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105520_8cf4b6fc0feb75748a28801a6e7aa0d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105520_8cf4b6fc0feb75748a28801a6e7aa0d6.png&h=80ec764c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於無其他相 透過2張相既推測<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/105551_c2e758ec1d4b65886c2e24eeddbe75c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F105551_c2e758ec1d4b65886c2e24eeddbe75c2.jpg&h=4a54c7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會員on99屌喇星就係前排中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}